# ============ Rust / Anchor ============
target/
.anchor/
test-ledger/

# Solana 1.18 side-install ledger dirs — created when the validator runs with
# `--ledger sv-118` from various subdirs. Multi-GB rocksdb state, never commit.
**/sv-118/

# Solana program upgrade authority keypairs — NEVER commit these.
# Anyone with these can replace the deployed program with arbitrary code.
**/*-keypair.json

